hemp
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Phormium tenax</i>, an obs name, used by early writers then reintroduced as a commercial name ?for the manufactured product of flax;  flax, also native hemp, New Zealand hemp.
